```

The old `WelcomeMessage` component and its CSS can be kept for backward compatibility or removed if desired.

### Animation Specifications

| Transition | Type | Stiffness | Damping | Duration |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Modal enter | spring | 400 | 30 | -- |
| Modal exit | tween | -- | -- | 0.2s |
| Slide enter/exit | spring | 300 | 28 | -- |
| Avatar pulse | keyframes | -- | -- | 2s repeat |
| Progress dot scale | spring | 400 | 25 | -- |
| Confetti | canvas-confetti | -- | -- | 500ms delay |

