## Part D: Onboarding Checklist / Progress Widget

### Architecture

A small floating card on the home feed that tracks onboarding milestones. Uses the shared onboarding context to read/write checklist state.

**New files:**
1. `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\Onboarding\Checklist\OnboardingChecklist.jsx`
2. `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\Onboarding\Checklist\ChecklistItem.jsx`
